{"tid":2373356,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下Ielts傳銷係咪呃人？hd上degree係咪一定要考Ielts？","createTime":"2021-01-20T11:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T04:10:15.000Z","uid":374459,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4560f51f89dfccb2a596487b97965c5d69cf0d82","tid":2373356,"uid":374459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:33:29.000Z","msg":"頭先收到一個3114字頭既電話<br />\n上網serach我見係Ielts推銷<br />\n一開始就純粹問下我DSE成績<br />\n之後就問下我有關升學果D野<br />\n咁答完佢一大輪之後呢🙄<br />\n佢就話咩如果hd升返degree<br />\n除咗gpa夠高跟住要睇英文DSE成績<br />\n然後佢就話咩Ielts有6.5<br />\n可以升唔知0.幾GPA🤔<br />\n跟住sell一個咩Ielts班免費試讀<br />\n佢係sales一定講到Ielts好重要咁樣😑<br />\n跟住又話咩約時間上去免費班<br />\n咩覺得ok可以交三百蚊留位費<br />\n我check post之前有人都中過招🧐<br />\n所以其實我就冇諗住埋佢既<br />\n開post主要想知Ielts係咪一定要考？<br />\n同埋有冇人真係有去過？<br />\n利申：polyhd yr1，英文3"},{"pid":"7b1e7f4b19069822e13d7820f7d8328e13778356","tid":2373356,"uid":263131,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:36:49.000Z","msg":"問翻所屬大學，有啲可以代替DSE成績，有啲一定要讀<br />\n外國清一色一定要IELTS/TOEFL to verify english proficiency<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f58d52f4b92ac6661dc9bff4b7e29d1c9740529","tid":2373356,"uid":198497,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:37:28.000Z","msg":"local升local唔使"},{"pid":"c4468519af887d76b6490a01cf39160666827c1c","tid":2373356,"uid":157074,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:39:26.000Z","msg":"唔一定要考視乎你學位嗰間大學嘅要求<br />\n但係考完剩係得兩年有效期<br />\n所以揀清楚咩時間去考<br />\n其實去上堂都冇咩壞處除咗要洗錢之外<br />\n學啲英文同平時DSE嗰啲唔同<br />\n就算你升嗰間大學冇需要考IELTS<br />\n都建議你就嚟畢業嘅時候可以去考<br />\n兩年有效期內拎住個證書可以繼續升學或者搵工<br />\n而且畢業前嘅英文程度一定係好過你之後返工先去考<br />\n成績都會靚啲"},{"pid":"ff5198813e0fad3b277d685125e7fbaeb8ff70ab","tid":2373356,"uid":200973,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248caf52787dcd525115fe6260fa42cfbb9e4f25","tid":2373356,"uid":214644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:47:45.000Z","msg":"可以自己考，唔一定要讀"},{"pid":"b936453873740a95bb0df2e9437495a293998294","tid":2373356,"uid":71462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:52:34.000Z","msg":"唔需要<br />\n利申 asso升hku <br />\ndse eng lv3"},{"pid":"7cb0464a5cbc8b0a7a66fcb85d251331ea5c8a2a","tid":2373356,"uid":201061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:53:46.000Z","msg":"唔使考"},{"pid":"0e9c04769f688b7a6bb23e62dc41b4fecb20f516","tid":2373356,"uid":374459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b936453873740a95bb0df2e9437495a293998294","tid":2373356,"uid":71462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:52:34.000Z","msg":"唔需要<br />\n利申 asso升hku <br />\ndse eng lv3"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:54:34.000Z","msg":"你gpa幾多？？"},{"pid":"66145de24a605d57e5cf96e983ed5326b291db96","tid":2373356,"uid":113546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T12:12:51.000Z","msg":"讀得hd 你認真諗下同6.5分嘅距離遠唔遠<br />\n事關你除咗應付功課考試r frd 仲要溫英文同操ielts <br />\n再睇返你dse英文拎幾分 有心有力有銀彈 咁先考慮下啦<br />\n<br />\n因為到你面試嘅時候 假設佢比有條件取錄你<br />\n其實都有段時間可以補返個6.5<br />\n利申 中過伏不了 佢啲所謂試堂 會講到好似好撚有用 <br />\n短時間幫到你掌握學英文嘅技巧同考試題型<br />\n但其實冇撚用"},{"pid":"5b2e78c1896a56b001e1f07b17862d40ec967ca6","tid":2373356,"uid":71462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e9c04769f688b7a6bb23e62dc41b4fecb20f516","tid":2373356,"uid":374459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b936453873740a95bb0df2e9437495a293998294","tid":2373356,"uid":71462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:52:34.000Z","msg":"唔需要<br />\n利申 asso升hku <br />\ndse eng lv3"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:54:34.000Z","msg":"你gpa幾多？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T12:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f04e3699ba76b6264d6394458f2ad67ea8e6c01","tid":2373356,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T12:26:03.000Z","msg":"Ielts 自己溫啦"},{"pid":"05a653e0f1cd9f9335db7feba28bd7fd2e4e1754","tid":2373356,"uid":7828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:46:29.000Z","msg":"以下呢間？<br />\n<br />\n各位DSE學生報讀任何課程前，請先查詢有關課程是否有<span class=\"green\">HKQF（香港資歷架構）</span>的認可，切勿因為一時大意誤信他人被騙。<br />\n<br />\n資歷名冊官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Findex.html&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia3No2vAooDXMO4YLrfRUzdI%3D&h=0d9185a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n資歷搜尋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Fsearch%2Fqr-search%2F&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia3No2vAooDXMO4YLrfRUzdI%3D&h=fe934322\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上傳銷或者詐騙的人，他們喜歡先入為主，不停感情勒索，裝作大家感情深厚<br />\n<br />\n帶你去見工：<br />\n「要為屋企人著想，賺多啲錢」<br />\n「讀大學冇用㗎，呢份工先有錢途」<br />\n「有錢途再追逐自己夢想都唔遲」<br />\n「好自私，只顧及讀書，真係好好好自私，錢又媽比，家境又5好，明知讀完得萬幾蚊，照顧5到屋企，你又讀得5勁，點解要讀？」<br />\n「問你要揀買樓定讀大學，又問你憑咩講話冇時間讀書（因為平時有出黎發夢）<br />\n<br />\n帶你去傳銷學校 ：<br />\n「我想你改變自己」<br />\n「唔好輕易放棄，放棄自己將來」<br />\n「ive/副學士/hd 冇用㗎」<br />\n「想識d有上進心嘅男仔」<br />\n「d顧問好嚴格，記得帶齊所有身份證明文件/證書」<br />\n「張證書有poly 認可㗎，你讀其他之後出嚟做嘢冇用點算」<br />\n（poly 你老母，打過去poly 話唔撚係，只係出席活動的證書，唔會有咩學歷證明，食屎啦臭雞)<br />\n<br />\n帶你去美容：<br />\n「我帶你去做facial呀/你陪我去做facial呀」<br />\n「我當你是朋友才給你這優惠」<br />\n<br />\n[轉貼］<br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[大學生小心職場陷阱] 小心有傳銷公司成員係交友app 扮係你朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164242%2Fpage%2F1&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia3No2vAooDXMO4YLrfRUzdI%3D&h=f7c18f1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n叫你去interview個個聲稱人工係每單Job計 每單job有4位數字，Interview個個就話係計人頭 教育同醫美都唔同計法，前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n教育分 1-5 6-30 31-465 （重有再上<br />\n1-5:$1000/1<br />\n6-30:$1800/1<br />\n31-465:$2400/1<br />\n<br />\n醫美就計%<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱自己唔會由個客手上拎錢<br />\n係客比錢pr公司搵到嘅合作機構<br />\n再由合作機構比返佣pr即係佢地<br />\n<br />\n中匯商業大廈18-20樓<br />\n19樓主要做interview / training，18/20樓好似係office<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/15/hcjw3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F15%2Fhcjw3E.png&h=fba48af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FXuxBB7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFXuxBB7.png&h=dffa07b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41c21057ea06bb75ef1849f4475f558c3efc598a","tid":2373356,"uid":27946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:51:29.000Z","msg":"唔一定要考<br />\n只係有多張證明好過無<br />\nGPA比較緊要"},{"pid":"d0d183377cc6fbe1536a8470ed8721c8013e7b46","tid":2373356,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T16:28:52.000Z","msg":"唔一定要<br />\n問返你要讀果間要求<br />\nGPA就係GPA<br />\nielts唔會加到你GPA"},{"pid":"e893f7b736ede146165d98b1570d665f40ce00d3","tid":2373356,"uid":78188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T16:35:37.000Z","msg":"乜都冇考過 interview都冇 升返ugc"},{"pid":"5ac971db7fc833584e36241c6c87e49eaf5d2bb9","tid":2373356,"uid":22741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T18:06:33.000Z","msg":"除非間u指明要有6.5/7<br />\n唔係考黎冇乜用<br />\n但考下幾舊水又唔係真係好難拎6.5/7<br />\n自己報就得 唔洗上咩班"},{"pid":"663dcf5091adcbf5f95fe095f915263cc0b0c8ab","tid":2373356,"uid":244105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T18:21:45.000Z","msg":"唔係DSE英文冇3先要考咩"},{"pid":"2dad532ff1e3a310e1ec8a770ff13efa79fcb87e","tid":2373356,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T14:00:13.000Z","msg":"唔一定要考<br />\n三大 business school既話 一般要lv4 或者 ielts band 7 <br />\n你dse 有3 可以focus \b喺gpa先"},{"pid":"7f966adbe1b94b6319ffecdcdc0b8b0d46b4b7cb","tid":2373356,"uid":204348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T04:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個間所謂ielts咨詢中心係<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">智權教育中心</span></span></strong><br />\n認撚住佢<br />\n<br />\n間野臨到考DSE季節會請同考生差唔多年紀既豬仔嚟做pt<br />\n職位叫「Consultant Assistant」<br />\n下面係間野既pt招聘<br />\n<a href=\"https://moovup.com/hk/job/兼職-consultant-assistant-油尖旺/19e3598e-c571-490b-a173-789222ead6f0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoovup.com%2Fhk%2Fjob%2F%E5%85%BC%E8%81%B7-consultant-assistant-%E6%B2%B9%E5%B0%96%E6%97%BA%2F19e3598e-c571-490b-a173-789222ead6f0%2F&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia3No2vAooDXMO4YLrfRUzdI%3D&h=ddf25fc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://moovup.com/hk/job/兼職-consultant-assistant-油尖旺/19e3598e-c571-490b-a173-789222ead6f0/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說佢收線之後 同你contact嗰個豬仔會whatsapp你啲所謂既information比你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qwa3V5M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqwa3V5M.png&h=f88f3dfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}